    "chapter_title": {
      "ar": "بَابُ مَنْ فَطَّرَ صَائِماً",
      "en": "Chapter 3 – The one who provides for the breaking the Fast of a Fasting-one"
    },
    "gradings": [
      "Allamah Baqir al-Majlisi: <span> مجهول   </span> - Mir‘at al ‘Uqul Fi Sharh Akhbar Al al Rasul (16/211)"
    ],
